thread.title: GOP, NRA clash over age limits for assault rifles

title: GOP, NRA clash over age limits for assault rifles
text:
GOP, NRA clash over age limits for assault rifles 12:52am GMT - 01:43 
Florida Governor Rick Scott urged state lawmakers on Friday to raise the age requirement to buy assault rifles after last week's school massacre, putting him, President Trump, and other Republicans in a rare dispute with the powerful NRA.
